&lt;img src=&quot;https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2576/d2576350.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;image&quot; /&gt;
&lt;figcaption&gt;
[閒聊] 李杜軒去當球評了？
&lt;/figcaption&gt;
